                      <span class="font-medium">Hizmet süresi ne kadardır?</span>
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 ${colorClass} transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                      </svg>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="px-4 pb-4">
