                  </details>
                  <details class="group ${bgClass} rounded-lg">
                    <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-4">
                      <span class="font-medium">Fiyatlandırma nasıl yapılıyor?</span>
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 ${colorClass} transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                      </svg>
